SPEECH BY PRESIDENT MUHAMMADU BUHARI AT THE SIGNING OF THE 2021 APPROPRIATION BILL AND THE 2020 FINANCE BILL INTO LAW ON THURSDAY DECEMBER 31, 2020 AT COUNCIL CHAMBERS, PRESIDENTIAL VILLA, ABUJA. 27    As a nation, we are currently confronted with diverse challenges at this time.  I commend the understanding, sacrifice and resilience of our people, both young and old.  I assure everyone that our hope and confidence of a greater future shall not be in vain. 